{"tid":1705131,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到咗今時今日 香港人係咪要自己整武器?","createTime":"2019-11-11T00:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T00:51:33.000Z","uid":126675,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"452c62a0e3917583e18239b1fffa9dc538a59f65","tid":1705131,"uid":126675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:29:37.000Z","msg":"其實好多美軍嘅field manual好有用，而且放晒喺網上面任睇，大家一齊學吓英文啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nImprovised munitions handbook<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gunfreezone.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/improvised-munitions-handbook.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gunfreezone.net%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F03%2Fimprovised-munitions-handbook.pdf&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BNqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=88fa79a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.gunfreezone.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/03/improvised-munitions-handbook.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n呢本書教士兵用平民接觸到嘅工具自制武器。你可以學到同整槍、迫擊炮、炸彈同手榴彈嘅英文生字。<br />\n<br />\nSpecial Forces Sniper Training and Employment<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bits.de/NRANEU/others/amd-us-archive/FM3-05.222%2803%29.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bits.de%2FNRANEU%2Fothers%2Famd-us-archive%2FFM3-05.222%252803%2529.pdf&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BNqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=97afb863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bits.de/NRANEU/others/amd-us-archive/FM3-05.222%2803%29.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n呢本書教一堆同狙擊手選擇安全嘅地方觀察同隱身有關嘅生字。<br />\n<br />\n之後呢度仲有一堆Ebook，教大家學同magic有關嘅生字。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://epdf.pub/search/C-220+Improvised+explosives+for+detonators\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepdf.pub%2Fsearch%2FC-220%2BImprovised%2Bexplosives%2Bfor%2Bdetonators&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BNqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=d6a579b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://epdf.pub/search/C-220+Improvised+explosives+for+detonators</a><br />\n<br />\nGRENADES AND PYROTECHNIC SIGNALS<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://armypubs.army.mil/ProductMaps/PubForm/Details.aspx?PUB_ID=103527\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farmypubs.army.mil%2FProductMaps%2FPubForm%2FDetails.aspx%3FPUB_ID%3D103527&d=UQnAMLTNR8x1T2wYrkOS%2BNqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=4378c864\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://armypubs.army.mil/ProductMaps/PubForm/Details.aspx?PUB_ID=103527</a><br />\n<br />\n最後呢本教大家同用手榴彈（同其他掉嘅嘢）有關嘅生字。"},{"pid":"547edaae37873497511d95bb818c2b8631202cd5","tid":1705131,"uid":126675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:30:03.000Z","msg":"利申: 我係歐洲<br />\n<br />\nMON POST狗唔洗check我IP喇"},{"pid":"b6ec5e9fda0beaf7acc2bf9b92b077a7628cb404","tid":1705131,"uid":288912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:31:38.000Z","msg":"我用最卑微嘅心，求吓咁多位<br />\n<br />\n香港人，忍無可忍！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1705050\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1705050</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c963c34ce924ba2dfb8f606f7e9a8a6e146a3b4f","tid":1705131,"uid":10466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T00:51:33.000Z","msg":"殺光黑警會，食狗肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}